                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14427828" author="michael-o" created="Sun, 2 Feb 2014 08:33:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed with &lt;tt&gt;r1563621&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14427797" author="hboutemy" created="Sun, 2 Feb 2014 09:45:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;each UTF-8 byte has been translated as a unicode character, instead of translating multi-byte characters&lt;br/&gt;
really fixed in &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1563641&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;r1563641&lt;/a&gt;: used &lt;tt&gt;iconv -f UTF-8 -t ISO-8859-1&lt;/tt&gt; to be sure&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14427844" author="michael-o" created="Sun, 2 Feb 2014 10:49:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looks good now but I have done the same with &lt;tt&gt;native2ascii&lt;/tt&gt; and both files are equivalent in terms of Properties spec.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14427723" author="hboutemy" created="Sun, 2 Feb 2014 11:34:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;notice: Portuguese is supported in ISO-8859-1 (see &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO/IEC_8859-1&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO/IEC_8859-1&lt;/a&gt;), so there is no problem with &#243; &#231; &#227; &#233; &#245; &#225; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;if you want, you can use &lt;tt&gt;native2ascii -encoding ISO-8859-1&lt;/tt&gt; from actual content to use unicode escapes (or use &lt;tt&gt;native2ascii -encoding UTF-8&lt;/tt&gt; from original UTF-8 content): that&apos;s only a matter of taste&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17970536" author="githubbot" created="Fri, 13 Jun 2025 09:40:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;jira-importer opened a new issue, #216:&lt;br/&gt;
URL: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-checkstyle-plugin/issues/216&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/maven-checkstyle-plugin/issues/216&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   **&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;Michael Osipov&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=michael-o)**&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=michael-o)**&lt;/a&gt; opened **&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MCHECKSTYLE-210&quot; title=&quot;Resource bundles have wrong file encoding&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MCHECKSTYLE-210&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MCHECKSTYLE-210&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;(&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MCHECKSTYLE-210?redirect=false)**&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MCHECKSTYLE-210?redirect=false)**&lt;/a&gt; and commented&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   Properties file for `pr_BR` is UTF-8 encoded but it should be ISO 8859-1.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;   &amp;#8212;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   *&lt;b&gt;Affects:&lt;/b&gt;* 2.11&lt;/p&gt;


</comment>
                            <comment id="17970537" author="githubbot" created="Fri, 13 Jun 2025 09:40:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;jira-importer commented on issue #216:&lt;br/&gt;
URL: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-checkstyle-plugin/issues/216#issuecomment-2969752075&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/maven-checkstyle-plugin/issues/216#issuecomment-2969752075&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   **&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;Herv&#233; Boutemy&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=hboutemy)**&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=hboutemy)**&lt;/a&gt; commented&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   each UTF-8 byte has been translated as a unicode character, instead of translating multi-byte characters&lt;br/&gt;
   really fixed in &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;r1563641&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1563641):&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1563641):&lt;/a&gt; used `iconv -f UTF-8 -t ISO-8859-1` to be sure&lt;/p&gt;


</comment>
                            <comment id="17970538" author="githubbot" created="Fri, 13 Jun 2025 09:40:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;jira-importer commented on issue #216:&lt;br/&gt;
URL: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-checkstyle-plugin/issues/216#issuecomment-2969752070&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/maven-checkstyle-plugin/issues/216#issuecomment-2969752070&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   **&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;Michael Osipov&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=michael-o)**&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=michael-o)**&lt;/a&gt; commented&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   Fixed with `r1563621`.&lt;/p&gt;


</comment>
                            <comment id="17970539" author="githubbot" created="Fri, 13 Jun 2025 09:40:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;jira-importer commented on issue #216:&lt;br/&gt;
URL: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-checkstyle-plugin/issues/216#issuecomment-2969752081&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/maven-checkstyle-plugin/issues/216#issuecomment-2969752081&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   **&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;Michael Osipov&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=michael-o)**&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=michael-o)**&lt;/a&gt; commented&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   Looks good now but I have done the same with `native2ascii` and both files are equivalent in terms of Properties spec.&lt;/p&gt;


</comment>
                            <comment id="17970540" author="githubbot" created="Fri, 13 Jun 2025 09:40:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;jira-importer commented on issue #216:&lt;br/&gt;
URL: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-checkstyle-plugin/issues/216#issuecomment-2969752089&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/maven-checkstyle-plugin/issues/216#issuecomment-2969752089&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   **&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;Herv&#233; Boutemy&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=hboutemy)**&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=hboutemy)**&lt;/a&gt; commented&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   notice: Portuguese is supported in ISO-8859-1 (see &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO/IEC_8859-1&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO/IEC_8859-1&lt;/a&gt;), so there is no problem with &#243; &#231; &#227; &#233; &#245; &#225;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;   if you want, you can use `native2ascii -encoding ISO-8859-1` from actual content to use unicode escapes (or use `native2ascii -encoding UTF-8` from original UTF-8 content): that&apos;s only a matter of taste&lt;/p&gt;


</comment>
